descriptionHtml:
[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1704/images/11542-2-1502660470.png[/img]
This is a medium sized player home. A Lakehouse Placed on Ilinalta lake and is currently still a WIP. Feel free to download and shoot suggestions my way. this is my first player home. the reason for the white on the trees is my texture i need to download some new ones XD. but this is all bare minimal atm more to come just stay tuned and drop some comments.

 -Ominious-

V.01
New Update includes

* New Map Marker

* Some Minor & major clipping

* Light Changes made in Enchanting room Lighting 

* Light Changes made In Alchemy Room

* New Movable Static and effects in Enchanting Room, Alchemy Room, Kitchen, Forge, And Icebox

* New BYOH Bard Taki Added to Main Area 

* More Flora And trees Added to outside 

* Added a Sitting area and wine for front porch

* Added More Clutter for Enchanting Room, Alchemy Room

* Removed Bandits And the two God Weapons in the back
 
  (Please always make sure to download the latest version) ALSO **** Will be working on a Skyrim Legendary Version Very soon.****


Please if there are any bugs errors or suggestions let me know I will be constantly working on this mod and updating thank you guys for Downloads! :)
author: Ominious
